{"title":"Markdown基本语法","date":"2019-10-25T04:39:57.702Z","link":"post/Markdown基本语法","updated":"2019-10-25T04:50:08.106Z","content":"<hr>\n<p>title:Markdown基本语法</p>\n<h2 id=\"date-2019-09-10\">date:2019-09-10<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#date-2019-09-10\"></a></h2><h1 id=\"Markdown基本语法\">Markdown基本语法<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#Markdown基本语法\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"1-标题\">1. 标题<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#1-标题\"></a></h2><p>一级标题：# + 空格 +标题名称 + 回车</p>\n<h1 id=\"一级标题\">一级标题<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#一级标题\"></a></h1><p>二级标题：## + 空格 +标题名称 + 回车</p>\n<h2 id=\"二级标题\">二级标题<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#二级标题\"></a></h2><p>三级标题：### + 空格 +标题名称 + 回车</p>\n<h3 id=\"三级标题\">三级标题<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#三级标题\"></a></h3><p>四级标题：#### + 空格 +标题名称 + 回车</p>\n<h4 id=\"四级标题\">四级标题<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#四级标题\"></a></h4><p>五级标题：##### + 空格 +标题名称 + 回车</p>\n<h5 id=\"五级标题\">五级标题<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#五级标题\"></a></h5><p>六级标题：###### + 空格 +标题名称 + 回车</p>\n<h6 id=\"六级标题\">六级标题<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#六级标题\"></a></h6><h2 id=\"2-字体\">2. 字体<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#2-字体\"></a></h2><h3 id=\"2-1-加粗\">2.1 加粗<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#2-1-加粗\"></a></h3><p>在字体两边用两个*号包围</p>\n<p><strong>Hello，World！</strong></p>\n<h3 id=\"2-2-斜体\">2.2 斜体<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#2-2-斜体\"></a></h3><p>在字体两边用一个 * 号包围</p>\n<p><em>Hello，World！</em></p>\n<h3 id=\"2-3-斜体加粗\">2.3 斜体加粗<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#2-3-斜体加粗\"></a></h3><p>在字体两边用三个 * 号包围</p>\n<p><strong><em>Hello，World！</em></strong></p>\n<h3 id=\"2-4-删除线\">2.4 删除线<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#2-4-删除线\"></a></h3><p>在字体两边用两个~号包围</p>\n<p><del>Hello，World！</del></p>\n<h2 id=\"3-引用\">3. 引用<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#3-引用\"></a></h2><p>‘&gt;’ + 空格</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>引用</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"4-分割线\">4. 分割线<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#4-分割线\"></a></h2><h3 id=\"4-1-‘—‘\">4.1 ‘—‘<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#4-1-‘—‘\"></a></h3><hr>\n<h3 id=\"4-2-‘-’\">4.2 ‘***’<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#4-2-‘-’\"></a></h3><hr>\n<h2 id=\"5-图片\">5. 图片<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#5-图片\"></a></h2><p> ‘ ! ‘ + ‘ [ ‘ + 图片名称(可自定义) + ‘ ] ‘ + ‘ ( ‘ + 图片地址(既可以是本地也可以是网络图片地址) + ‘ ) ‘</p>\n<p><img src=\"C:%5CUsers%5CHP%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5C1571974131922.png\" alt=\"1571974131922\" class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"6-超链接\">6. 超链接<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#6-超链接\"></a></h2><p>‘ [ ‘ + 超链接标题 + ‘ ] ‘ + ‘ ( ‘ + 链接地址 + ‘ ) ‘</p>\n<p><a href=\"https:www.baidu.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">点击跳转到超链接</a></p>\n<p>注：Markdown不支持在链接中打开新页面，但是网站中可以</p>\n<h2 id=\"7-列表\">7. 列表<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#7-列表\"></a></h2><h3 id=\"7-1-有序列表\">7.1 有序列表<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#7-1-有序列表\"></a></h3><p>数字 + 空格 + 回车</p>\n<ol>\n<li></li>\n<li></li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"7-2-无序列表\">7.2 无序列表<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#7-2-无序列表\"></a></h3><p>减号’-‘ + 空格 + 回车</p>\n<ul>\n<li></li>\n<li></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"8-表格\">8. 表格<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#8-表格\"></a></h2><h3 id=\"8-1列名-列名-列名-…\">8.1列名|列名|列名|…<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#8-1列名-列名-列名-…\"></a></h3><p>–|–|–|…|</p>\n<p>数据|数据|数据|<br>–|–|–|…|</p>\n<p>…|…|…|…|</p>\n<p>注：需要到源代码模式下将行间空白删除</p>\n<p> 列名|列名|列名|…<br> –|–|–|–|–<br> 数据|数据|数据|…<br> –|–|–|…<br> …|…|…|…</p>\n<h3 id=\"8-2-右键插入表格-快捷键Ctrl-T\">8.2 右键插入表格/快捷键Ctrl+T<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#8-2-右键插入表格-快捷键Ctrl-T\"></a></h3><h2 id=\"9-代码\">9. 代码<a href=\"post/Markdown基本语法#9-代码\"></a></h2><p>“ <figure class=\"highlight plain\"><figcaption><span>+ 编程语言</span></figcaption><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">```Java</span><br><span class=\"line\">public static void main(String[] args&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    System.out.println(&quot;Hello World!&quot;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    System.out.println(&quot;Hello Markdown!&quot;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n","next":{"title":"300分钟算法笔记","link":"post/300分钟算法笔记"},"plink":"http://YIzzzzz.github.io/post/Markdown基本语法/","toc":[{"title":"一级标题","id":"一级标题","index":"1","children":[{"title":"二级标题","id":"二级标题","index":"1.1","children":[{"title":"三级标题","id":"三级标题","index":"1.1.1"}]},{"title":"2. 字体","id":"2-字体","index":"1.2","children":[{"title":"2.1 加粗","id":"2-1-加粗","index":"1.2.1"},{"title":"2.2 斜体","id":"2-2-斜体","index":"1.2.2"},{"title":"2.3 斜体加粗","id":"2-3-斜体加粗","index":"1.2.3"},{"title":"2.4 删除线","id":"2-4-删除线","index":"1.2.4"}]},{"title":"3. 引用","id":"3-引用","index":"1.3"},{"title":"4. 分割线","id":"4-分割线","index":"1.4","children":[{"title":"4.1 ‘—‘","id":"4-1-‘—‘","index":"1.4.1"},{"title":"4.2 ‘***’","id":"4-2-‘-’","index":"1.4.2"}]},{"title":"5. 图片","id":"5-图片","index":"1.5"},{"title":"6. 超链接","id":"6-超链接","index":"1.6"},{"title":"7. 列表","id":"7-列表","index":"1.7","children":[{"title":"7.1 有序列表","id":"7-1-有序列表","index":"1.7.1"},{"title":"7.2 无序列表","id":"7-2-无序列表","index":"1.7.2"}]},{"title":"8. 表格","id":"8-表格","index":"1.8","children":[{"title":"8.1列名|列名|列名|…","id":"8-1列名-列名-列名-…","index":"1.8.1"},{"title":"8.2 右键插入表格/快捷键Ctrl+T","id":"8-2-右键插入表格-快捷键Ctrl-T","index":"1.8.2"}]},{"title":"9. 代码","id":"9-代码","index":"1.9"}]}]}